    {
      "end": 44.7400016784668,
      "text": "or plans that, or knows that, except you, and when you don't say any of that, how do you know,",
      "start": 36.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 55.540000915527344,
      "text": "how do you know what others feel, or are you aware of anything other than narcissistic flair,",
      "start": 45.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 65.81999969482422,
      "text": "because if you're found, then you're found, and you won't second guess, feel different ways,",
      "start": 57.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 72.63999938964844,
      "text": "feel guilt, tell everybody else they're this way, and that they're not good enough to pass",
      "start": 66.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 83.83999633789062,
      "text": "your own test, well neither are you, and that's the way that you critically be in tune with you,",
      "start": 72.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 89.12000274658203,
      "text": "because no one's good enough for you, but neither are you,",
      "start": 83.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 101,
      "text": "so just relate, instead of taking it down to the bottom of all your fears and dreams,",
      "start": 92.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 109.5999984741211,
      "text": "that you can't put to the forefront, the things that you think define your life,",
      "start": 101.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 117.55999755859375,
      "text": "what defines you, no to you, cause you say you know, and you say you know it all,",
